To cite package ‘torchopt’ in publications use:

  Gilberto Camara, Rolf Simoes, Daniel Falbel, Felipe Souza and Alber Sanchez (NA).
  torchopt: Advanced Optimizers for Torch. R package version 0.1.2.
  https://github.com/e-sensing/torchopt/

A BibTeX entry for LaTeX users is

  @Manual{,
    title = {torchopt: Advanced Optimizers for Torch},
    author = {Gilberto Camara and Rolf Simoes and Daniel Falbel and Felipe Souza and Alber Sanchez},
    note = {R package version 0.1.2},
    url = {https://github.com/e-sensing/torchopt/},
  }
